On Mon, Jun 07, 1999 at 02:46:44PM +0200, Martin Mares wrote:
>    I'd like to hear the opinion of PPC people, because in case we can get
> automatic conversion LE->BE at no extra cost, DaveM's argument about
> readl_be() being just extra complexity with no benefits is perfectly
> correct.
On MIPS endian conversion isn't supported in kernel mode.  Some chipsets
however have external per device endian conversion, most don't.  So the
conversion is usually done in software.
  Ralf
